34:47.853 --> 34:49.822
it affects
cognitive development,

34:49.856 --> 34:53.359
social competence,
the ability to trust.

34:53.393 --> 34:56.129
Some studies have even linked

34:56.161 --> 34:59.766
the father's involvement
to a higher I. Q.

34:59.800 --> 35:02.669
Paternal involvement
during middle childhood

35:02.703 --> 35:05.639
has been known to have
a positive effect

35:05.672 --> 35:07.207
on school success.

35:07.240 --> 35:10.210
Your Honor, these studies
are as sobering

35:10.243 --> 35:12.145
as they are unanimous.

35:12.178 --> 35:16.149
Fatherless kids are
more susceptible to depression,

35:16.182 --> 35:20.687
more likely to commit crimes,
to drop out of school,

35:20.721 --> 35:22.789
to commit suicide,

35:22.823 --> 35:25.859
11 times more likely
to be violent,

35:25.892 --> 35:28.695
more likely
to abuse drugs.

35:28.729 --> 35:31.765
Does this mean
a single mother

35:31.798 --> 35:34.768
