35:46.747 --> 35:49.650
is that this child
will be better off

35:49.683 --> 35:52.519
with a connection
to her dad.

35:52.553 --> 35:54.187
All we're asking for

35:54.220 --> 35:57.190
is that he be allowed
to be involved.

35:57.223 --> 36:01.895
