37:16.503 --> 37:18.371
I read all those studies,

37:18.404 --> 37:20.841
I spoke with several experts,

37:20.874 --> 37:22.843
and Ms. Garrett's right.

37:22.876 --> 37:26.379
Better the child have
some connection to her father,

37:26.412 --> 37:28.949
better he be involved
in her life

37:28.982 --> 37:30.416
right from the start.

37:30.450 --> 37:32.919
That's the best-case scenario,

37:32.953 --> 37:36.757
but that scenario wasn't
available to Ellenor Frutt.

37:36.790 --> 37:38.491
She wasn't with a man.

37:38.525 --> 37:40.927
She decided she wanted
to be a single parent,

37:40.961 --> 37:42.863
so she went to a friend

37:42.896 --> 37:45.498
and asked him
to be a donor.

37:45.532 --> 37:47.500
