38:16.029 --> 38:18.999
There are plenty of studies
to show

38:19.032 --> 38:21.535
the damage
caused to a child

38:21.568 --> 38:25.539
when a bond is broken
once a parent takes off.

38:25.572 --> 38:27.741
We maintain it's a risk

38:27.774 --> 38:31.344
letting this baby become
emotionally attached

38:31.377 --> 38:32.979
to Mr. Hale.

38:33.013 --> 38:35.481
