42:21.341 --> 42:23.977
and I just don't know...

42:24.010 --> 42:29.850
and I don't like to rule
on statistical probabilities.

42:29.883 --> 42:33.654
Without clear
and convincing evidence,

42:33.687 --> 42:39.159
